ard game)|Just One]]\n*[[Lord of the Rings (board game)|Lord of the Rings]]\n*[[Pandemic (board game)|Pandemic]]\n*[[Sentinels of the Multiverse]]\n*[[Shadows Over Camelot|Shadows over Camelot]]\n*[[Space Alert]]\n*[[X-COM]]\n}}\n\n==Word games==\nThese games are based on construction of words to score points.\n\n{{columns-list|colwidth=18em|\n*[[25 Words or Less]]\n*[[Acronymble]]\n*[[Aksharit]]\n*[[Alfapet]]\n*[[Bananagrams]]\n*[[Big Taboo]]\n*[[Kings Cribbage]]\n*[[Mad Gab]]\n*[[Pictionary]]\n*[[Probe (parlor game)|Probe]]\n*[[Scrabble]]\n*[[Thiruthamizh]]\n*[[Trickster (board game)|Trickster]]\n*[[UpWords]]\n*[[Words with Friends]]\n}}\n\n==Gaming systems==\nThese are sets that can be used to play multiple games.\n\n{{columns-list|colwidth=18em|\n*[[Flibbix]]\n*[[Hanafuda]]\n*[[Icehouse pieces]]\n*[[Stonehenge (game)|Stonehenge]]\n}}\n\n==See also==\n*[[Game of the Year]]\n*[[Games 100]]\n*[[List of board wargames]]\n*[[List of Japanese board games]]\n*[[List of mancala games]]\n*[[List of board game publishers]]\n*[[List of game manufacturers]]\n*[[List of cross and circle games]]\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.boardgamegeek.com Board Game Geek]\n*[http://www.boardgames.org Boardgames.org]\n*[http://zenseeker.net/BoardGames/ A Zen Guide to Board Games]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20120729010243/http://gamerate.net/board-card/ Gamerate Game database]\n*[https://boardgamesland.com Board Games Land]\n\n[[Category:Lists of games|Board games]]\n[[Category:Board games|*]]\n", "name_user": "GenralSupremoCB", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(I added Monopoly to this list.)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_board_games"}
